openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Media Range API
  version: 0.0.1
paths:
  /post-media-range:
    post:
      summary: Post media-range body
      operationId: post-media-range
      requestBody:
          description: media image
          content:
            'text/plain':
              schema:
                type: string
            'text/*':
              schema:
                type: string
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: integer
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
